Ask HN: Two women I referred to a company were bullied out
text:
Hello,

I referred two highly qualified women to work at a major company known worldwide who are attempting to IPO. They were subjected to direct and indirect harassment and bullying despite performing extremely well.

One of them finally quit and emailed the ceo of this company and cleared spelled out why she leaving due to bullying and requested an investigation.

They didn’t seem to do anything about it. I had to watch this and keep my mouth shut because I needed a job. I am still deeply angry at how they were treated and how the new ceo is talking about this on twitter.

The executive who did it is still at this company and now they are on twitter talking about how great at D&I they are.

I have the email she sent to the ceo. Should I share this email with the media?
